patch.comment: Bump minimatch from 10.1.2 to 10.2.1

Add `"node"` condition before `"import"` in the `"exports"` map so that Node.js uses the CJS output (which handles extensionless imports), while bundlers still use ESM via `"import"`. Fixes https://github.com/microsoft/rushstack/issues/5644.

minor.comment: Normalize package layout. CommonJS is now under `lib-commonjs`, DTS is now under `lib-dts`, and ESM is now under `lib-esm`. Imports to `lib` still work as before, handled by the `"exports"` field in `package.json`.

patch.comment: Update minimatch dependency from 10.0.3 to 10.1.2

minor.comment: Normalize import of builtin modules to use the `node:` protocol.

patch.comment: Upgrades the minimatch dependency from ~3.0.3 to 10.0.3 across the entire Rush monorepo to address a Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS) vulnerability in the underlying brace-expansion dependency.
Include CHANGELOG.md in published releases again
Include missing `type` modifiers on type-only exports.
Fix line endings in published package.
Update type-only imports to include the type modifier.

minor.comment: Update @types/node from 14 to 18

patch.comment: Update Webpack peerDependency to ~4.47.0.
Change the peer dependency selector on `@types/node` to a wildcard (`*`).

minor.comment: Bump @types/node peerDependency to ^14.18.36.
Move the @types/node dependency to an optional peerDependency.

patch.comment: Updating webpack/loader-utils to resolve github advisory CVE-2022-37601. https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-76p3-8jx3-jpfq

minor.comment: Add an option to output typings to additional output folders.

patch.comment: Rename from @rushstack/localization-plugin.
Bump @types/webpack

minor.comment: (BREAKING CHANGE) Move the `ignoreString` option from the `typingsGeneration` object to the root of the options object. It is now used to remove strings from both typings and from loc file parsing.
Add the ability to tweak string comments in generated typings.
Include an option to ignore strings from typings generation.
Extract utilities to @rushstack/localization-utilitiles.
Add support for .resjson files

patch.comment: Rename the "master" branch to "main".

minor.comment: Add an option to ignore missing RESX comments.
(BREAKING CHANGE) Remove "filesToIgnore" option in favor of "globsToIgnore."
Accept .resx.json as an alternative strings file extension.

patch.comment: Update the package.json repository field to include the directory property.

minor.comment: Use ITerminal instead of Terminal to allow for compatibility with other versions of @rushstack/node-core-library.

patch.comment: Upgrade the `@types/node` dependency to version to version 12.

minor.comment: Fix parameter name typo.
Upgrade @types/tapable
Update Webpack dependency to ~4.44.2

patch.comment: Update README.md
Handle webpack dev server hot updates.
Update typings generator dependency.
Updated project to build with Heft
Fix broken peer dependency specifier
Fix specification of optional peerDependencies.
Fix the way the loc file typings are generated in watch mode for large projects.
Make @types/webpack an optionalPeerDependency instead of a peerDependency.
Fix an issue where the localization plugin would throw if resolveMissingTranslatedStrings returns undefined for a locale.
Remove unnecessary jju dependency.
Fix encoding of tab characters.
Don't trim RESX text elements.
Fix an issue where the chunk URL generation code would mark some localized chunks as non-localized.
Fix an issue where some characters weren't escaped correctly.
Fix sourcemap filenames.

minor.comment: Add support for normalization of newlines in RESX files.
Fix a few RESX parsing issues and improve translated strings resolution.

patch.comment: Replace dependencies whose NPM scope was renamed from `@microsoft` to `@rushstack`
Extract the TypingsGenerator logic to a new package.

minor.comment: Initial implementation of plugin.
